reviewText: This movie sorta has the Plan 9 From Outer Space thing going...so horrible it's hillarious. I don't know if this was supposed to be a horror movie with some comedy elements or a comedy with horror elements but all I know is I was on the floor laughing. Just look at the in jokes and dialogue "Free at last , free at last , thank God almighty free at last" should be enough to get the NAACP protesting. "A friend with weed is a friend indeed"..HILLARIOUS..don't watch films like this wanting a brilliant filmmaking achievement , watch it when you need a good chuckle..and if you have a good sense of humor
A great comedy.  Probably the funniest of the Leprechaun videos yet.  A must see for the adult fan.  Lucky Charms is back again.
